column5: Due to most of the consumer shows being cancelled again this winter, I got to go ice fishing a lot more this year! I didn't really think about it in the past but I normally spend about 6 weeks of my winter at trade shows! Now I spend it on the ice LOL! Still a few weeks more!
Very nice David, you done well, congratulations. It doesn't appear you're complaining for having more time to spend on the ice. Good luck in the future.
Another guy posing with a ling. WTH?????????????? LOL Nice pics David.
Still gotta get out on the hard water some time dave
Very nice season so far for sure!!
Nice Thanks for sharing the pictures
I'm guessing they made for some fine dining David. Good stuff.
awesome pics! I got out today as well...not ready for ice season to end just yet. Hope to get the kids out next week during March Break
